headline: Truist Lowers GitLab (GTLB) PT to $75, Maintains Buy Rating
summary: GitLab Inc. (NASDAQ:GTLB) is one of the best technology stocks according to Wall Street analysts. Earlier on June 12, Truist adjusted the price target for GitLab to $75 from $80, while maintaining a Buy rating on the shares. This revision comes after GitLab’s Q1 2025 results, which, although exceeding guidance, did not meet investor expectations […]

headline: Truist Flags PayPal as a Weak Bet, Targets $68
